            <h2>3. Degree</h2>
            <p>The science students can select fields with Mathematics or with Biology. If you are interested in Mathematics you can select fields related to Engineering. Students interested in Biology take upMedicallyl related fields. There are numerous opportunities for science students.</p>
            <p><b>-B.Sc. </b>Bachelor of Science
                B.Sc. offers theoretical and practical knowledge about different subject areas. It covers all the main streams of Science. </p>
            <p><b>-BCA</b>Bachelor of Computer Applications is an undergraduate degree course in the field of Computer Applications. Few students use online or distance education programs to pursue this degree. BCA distance education the course has great career options for the students after they complete it.</p>
            <b>-BSc. Medical Laboratory Technology</b> <br>
            <b>-BSc. Cardiac Laboratory Technology </b><br> 
            <b>-BSc. Dialysis Technology </b> <br>
            <b>-Bsc agriculture </b> <br>
            <b>-BSc biotechnology</b> <br>
            <b>-B Pharma</b> </p><br>
  
